9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Winter in Sokcho | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"In the snowy seaside town of Sokcho, 25-year-old Soo-Ha works at a guesthouse. She drifts between her mother’s fish stall and her boyfriend until a French artist’s arrival stirs questions about her identity. As winter deepens, Soo-Ha and the artist form an unspoken connection through food and art."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110898/winter-in-sokcho"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Winter in Sokcho"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"In the snowy seaside town of Sokcho, 25-year-old Soo-Ha works at a guesthouse. She drifts between her mother’s fish stall and her boyfriend until a French artist’s arrival stirs questions about her identity. As winter deepens, Soo-Ha and the artist form an unspoken connection through food and art."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110898/winter-in-sokcho"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tVF00d1iCOpEnPx73tUGzsh1uaV.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Winter in Sokcho"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"In the snowy seaside town of Sokcho, 25-year-old Soo-Ha works at a guesthouse. She drifts between her mother’s fish stall and her boyfriend until a French artist’s arrival stirs questions about her identity. As winter deepens, Soo-Ha and the artist form an unspoken connection through food and art."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content